Original: Ah, that request? The client is that
spirited girl there. That hood she
wears is the most precious thing...!
[Page]
Be sure to talk to her and hear her
story. I shall await your swift
return...

Original: I heard that you found the storied
Finest Plains. Very well done!
[Page]
Our darling customer seemed satisfied
with your work as well.
[Page]
Perhaps your fame will spread in her
homeland as well, and you will become
even busier than you are now...!

Original: You detect a sweet, fragrant scent of
grass wafting from somewhere.
[Page]
You look down and discover that the
fruity bouquet is arising from the
green fields below.
[Page]
This must be the place where the
client said the best feed could be
gathered... the [Color:5]Finest Plains[Color:0]!
[Page]
You should return to the bar and
give the eager farmer their location.
Then the request will be complete!
